{"tid":1651444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班放負撚遲早搞輸場運動","createTime":"2019-10-13T10:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T12:35:51.000Z","uid":301632,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a760fbb6e9057133df4581cfbfea68e3991fe5db","tid":1651444,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:48:15.000Z","msg":"你啲放負撚<br />\n日日就話 呢樣做得唔好 個樣做得唔好<br />\n不停話冇人出 <br />\n有人搞活動又話活動冇意思<br />\n文宣出得差又屌屌屌<br />\n冇建議 只係話「再係咁就輸」<br />\n<br />\n又話今日好多手足比人拉<br />\n屌手足plan得差 又怪自己人<br />\n根本係因為啲狗改戰術 鳩拉<br />\n而家佢哋成功啦 你班仆街幾撚灰呀<br />\n<br />\n日日就喺度話 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輸輸輸</span></span><br />\n屌你老母你涼住冷氣喺屋企出放負post就緊係輸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成撚日就係度話輸 出面做緊嘢啲手足點諗呀<br />\n「我博條命出嚟又比你屌話做得唔夠，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁我做嚟做乜？</span></strong></span>」<br />\n就係比你哋搞到有心變冇心機做嘢<br />\n咪自然冇人出囉<br />\n<br />\n再有呢班放負垃圾<br />\n真係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">遲早輸</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n講完。"},{"pid":"0329899f6935ba6cd91af39c3cc5c42878ab2dfc","tid":1651444,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:48:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c50bbb32e19880598e59bc984174a69dc7a3095f","tid":1651444,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:48:56.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"87513a3b5f6d9641c2f699a3c3fd55b186224739","tid":1651444,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:48:59.000Z","msg":"輸晒你地老母"},{"pid":"3b0b90b6e47ba4102120ef1b4c7b7c0aff64b6e8","tid":1651444,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9335657601c6e7a14cc1edb71d372fb84135546","tid":1651444,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"五毛嚟玩分化姐"},{"pid":